  "summary": "「她山之石」新增： 寫作很難，因爲寫的過程就是學的過程。如果 AI 消滅了難度，也就消滅了學習。 ——Rose […]",
  "content": "<p>「<a href=\"https://blog.yitianshijie.net/quotes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">她山之石</a>」新增：</p>\n<blockquote><p>寫作很難，因爲寫的過程就是學的過程。如果 AI 消滅了難度，也就消滅了學習。</p></blockquote>\n<p>——Rose Horowitch, <a href=\"https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/2026/08/reading-crisis-postliterate-age/687618/#:~:text=Writing%20is%20hard%20because%20the%20writer%20is%20learning.%20If%20AI%20eliminates%20the%20challenge%2C%20it%20also%20eliminates%20the%20learning.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2026</a> (付費後可讀)</p>",
